OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773162679
OL,3,CThree injured after double-decker bus
OL,4,Ccollides with bridge
OL,6,FThree people have been injured after a
OL,7,Fdouble decker bus hit a bridge in
OL,8,FReading.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FLoddon Bridge Road in Woodley just
OL,12,Fafter 9am on Monday morning. (9 March)
OL,14,FPolice say the driver suffered a
OL,15,Fmedical episode.
OL,17,FTwo people, a woman in her 80s and a
OL,18,Fwoman in her 40s were taken to the
OL,19,FRoyal Berkshire Hospital for treatment
OL,20,Fand a teenager was treated by
OL,21,Fparamedics at the scene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
