CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773162679
OL,3,CThree injured after double-decker bus
OL,4,Ccollides with bridge
OL,6,FITV Meridian has approached Reading
OL,7,FBuses.
OL,9,FA spokesman for Thames Valley Police
OL,10,Fconfirmed officers were called to
OL,11,FLoddon Bridge Road shortly after 9am
OL,12,Ffollowing a crash. The bus driver was
OL,13,Ftaken to hospital to be assessed.
OL,15,FA spokesman for the South Central
OL,16,FAmbulance Service confirmed that crews
OL,17,Fwere called to a "sizaeable incident"
OL,18,Fand it was fortunate there weren't
OL,19,Fmany people on the bus at the time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
