FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773162679
OL,3,CThree injured after double-decker bus
OL,4,Ccollides with bridge
OL,6,F"We received a call from the Royal
OL,7,FBerkshire Fire & Rescue Service at
OL,8,F09:17 informing us that a bus had
OL,9,Fcollided with a bridge on Loddon Road
OL,10,Fin Woodley.
OL,12,F"We were informed that in addition to
OL,13,Fthe male driver, there were three
OL,14,Fpassengers on board at the time of the
OL,15,Fcollision.
OL,17,F"We sent four ambulances and a
OL,18,Fparamedic team leader in a rapid
OL,19,Fresponse vehicle to the incident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
