OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773162679
OL,3,CThree injured after double-decker bus
OL,4,Ccollides with bridge
OL,6,F"Two passengers - a female aged in her
OL,7,F80s and a female in her 40s had
OL,8,Fsustained facial injuries and were
OL,9,Ftaken to the Royal Berkshire Hospital.
OL,10,FThe third passenger was a teenager who
OL,11,Fhad sustained minor injuries and was
OL,12,Ftreated and discharged on scene to go
OL,13,Fhome with their parents.
OL,15,F"The male driver may have sustained a
OL,16,Fmedical episode at the wheel and has
OL,17,Falso been taken to RBH for further
OL,18,Fassessment and treatment."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
